reviews.review_text: Terrific Show! This is a fantastic recording of an absolutely terrific show! Give it a try, you won't be disapointed. It's worthy of all five stars in my opinion.  Thanks for putting this one out there, you really made my day!

What?? This is a great show and an o.k. audience recording.  It is full of the hiss and crowd noise typical of most audience recordings.  If that is your thing you will like this show.  I personally like the matrix that is available and wouldn't even give that 5 stars. I must overcorrect for the first post and give this 3 stars.
Nice bright recording, high-energy show This is an above average aud recording for sure. Lots of range, not too noisy at all. Great crowd and a tight and energetic performance all the way.
